            "title": "盤中速報 - 皇昌(2543)大漲7.15%，報65.9元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>皇昌(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2543:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2543\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2543-TW</a>)22日13:15股價上漲4.4元，報65.9元，漲幅7.15%，成交2,035張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>皇昌(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2543:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2543\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2543-TW</a>)所屬產業為建材營造業，主要業務為土木建築工程之承攬業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌2.38%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-620 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-468 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-152 張</li> <li>融資增減：-409 張</li> <li>融券增減：-47 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
